<L>Which in my doubting mind create</L>
<L>Conformity to church and &s;tate,</L>
<L>I go, pur&s;uant to my plan,</L>
<L>To Mecca with the caravan,</L>
<L><PB N="129" REF="131">And think it right in common &s;en&s;e</L>
<L>Both for diver&s;ion and defence.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Reforming &s;chemes are none of mine;</L>
<L>To mend the world's a va&s;t de&s;ign:</L>
