</LG>
<LG>
<L>Since di&s;appointment galls within,</L>
<L>And &s;ubjugates the &s;oul to Spleen,</L>
<L>Mo&s;t &s;chemes, as money-&s;nares, I hate,</L>
<L>And bite not at projector's bait.</L>
<L>Sufficient wrecks appear each day,</L>
<L>And yet fre&s;h fools are ca&s;t away.</L>
<L>Ere well the bubbled can turn round,</L>
<L>Their painted ve&s;&s;el runs aground;</L>
<L>Or in deep &s;eas it over&s;ets</L>
