<L><PB N="143" REF="145">I many a notion take to ta&s;k,</L>
<L>Made dreadful by its vi&s;or-ma&s;k.</L>
<L>Thus &s;cruple, &s;pa&s;m of the mind,</L>
<L>Is cur'd, and certainty I find,</L>
<L>Since optick rea&s;on &s;hews me plain,</L>
<L>I dreaded &s;pectres of the brain,</L>
<L>And legendary fears are gone,</L>
