<LG>
<L><NOTE N="n" PLACE="foot"><L>Aut famam &s;equere, aut &s;ibi convenientia finge,</L>
<L>Scriptor honoratum &s;i forte reponis Achillem,</L>
<L>Impiger, iracundus, inexorabilis, acer,</L>
