<L>Make to it&s;elf the flying &s;quadron true.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L><NOTE N="p" PLACE="foot"><L>Difficile e&s;t proprie communia dicere: tuque</L>
<L>Rectius Iliacum carmen deducis in actus,</L>
<L>Quam &s;i proferres ignota indictaque primus.</L>
<L>Publica materies privati juris erit, &s;i</L>
<L>Nec circa vilem patulumque moraberis orbem.</L>
<L>Nec verbum verbo curabis redd&eacute;re fidus</L>
<L>Interpres; nec de&s;ilies imitator in arctum,</L>
