<L>"Dic mihi Mu&s;a virum, captae po&s;t tempora Trojae,</L>
<L>"Qui mores hominum multorum vidit &amp; urbes.</L></NOTE>With art and mode&s;ty your part maintain;</L>
<L>And talk like Col'nel Titus, not like Lane.</L>
