</LG>
<LG>
<PB N="266" REF="268">
<L><NOTE N="r" PLACE="foot"><L>Non fumum ex fulgore, &s;ed ex fumo dare lucem</L>
<L>Cogitat &mdash;</L></NOTE>Some mighty blu&s;terers impeach with noi&s;e,</L>
<L>And call their private cry, the publick voice.</L>
<L><NOTE N="s" PLACE="foot"><L>Quid dignum tanto feret hic promi&s;&s;or hiatu?</L>
