</LG>
<LG>
<L><NOTE N="t" PLACE="foot"><L>Nec reditum Diomedes ab interitu Meleagri,</L>
<L>Nec gemino bellum Trojanum orditur ab ovo;</L>
<L>&mdash; &amp; quae</L>
<L>De&s;perat tractata nite&s;cere po&s;&s;e, relinquit;</L>
