<L>Mobilibu&s;que decor naturis dandus &amp; annis.</L></NOTE>If when you &s;peak, you'd hear a needle fall,</L>
<L>And make the frequent hear-hims rend the wall,</L>
<L>In matters &s;uited to your ta&s;te engage,</L>
<L>Rememb'ring &s;till your quality and age.</L>
<L>Thy ta&s;k be this, young knight, and hear my &s;ong,</L>
