</LG>
<LG>
<PB N="267" REF="269">
<L><NOTE N="x" PLACE="foot"><L>Reddere qui voces jam &s;cit puer, &amp; pede certo</L>
<L>Signat humum, je&s;tis paribus colludere, &amp; iram</L>
