<L><PB N="268" REF="270">With men in pow'r &s;trict friend&s;hip we pur&s;ue,</L>
<L>With &s;ome con&s;iderable po&s;t in view.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>A man of forty years to change his note,</L>
<L>One way to &s;peak, and t'other way to vote;</L>
