<L>And old Sir John with Polly Peachum walk.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L><NOTE N="b" PLACE="foot"><L>Aut agitur res in &s;cenis, aut acta refertur.</L>
<L>Segnius irritant animos demi&s;&s;a per aures,</L>
<L>Qu&agrave;m quae &s;unt oculis &s;ubjecta fidelibus, &amp; quae</L>
<L>Ip&s;e &s;ibi tradit &s;pectator.</L>
<L>Quodcunque o&s;tendis mihi &s;ic, incredulus odi.</L></NOTE>Now as to double, or to fal&s;e returns,</L>
