<LG>
<L><NOTE N="e" PLACE="foot"><L>Tibia non, ut nunc Orichalcho vincta, tubaeque</L>
<L>Aemula, &s;ed tenuis &s;implex foramine pauco</L>
<L>A&s;pirare, &amp; ade&s;&s;e choris erat utilis, &amp;c.</L>
<L>Po&s;tquam coepit agros extendere victor, &amp; urbem</L>
<L>Latior amplecti murus, &amp;c.</L>
<L>Acce&s;&s;it numeri&s;que modi&s;que licentia major;</L>
<L>Sic etiam fidibus voces crevere &s;everis,</L>
